Package seng202.team5.map

Class Bounds

java.lang.Object
seng202.team5.map.Bounds
public class Bounds
extends java.lang.Object
Bounds is an object that represents a rectangular region between two points on the world map. It starts from the "southwest" point then covers all the space going northeast to the "northeast" point.
